snippet.title: EVERY DEVLOG EVER
snippet.description:
I made a rhythm game in 48 hours (wow so cool). This is a devlog about that game (yeah).

-------------------------------------------------------- 

Links: 

Play the game here:
https://agent-jo.itch.io/sea-garden

Check out my game Salvo Shuffle:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2579550?utm_source=youtube

Join my discord server:
https://discord.com/invite/J4mvAahm6J

My music on Newgrounds: 
https://agentjo.newgrounds.com/ 

My games on Steam and Itch: 
https://store.steampowered.com/curator/44561361
https://agent-jo.itch.io/ 
 
--------------------------------------------------------  

Chapters: 
0:00 Intro 
1:51 Day 1
2:28 Stream
3:46 Day 2 
5:49 Day 3
7:18 Voting
7:46 Results
8:56 Outro

--------------------------------------------------------

Music used (in order):
Mario Kart 8 Deluxe - Sunshine Airport
Dohna Dohna - Easy as Pie
A Hat in Time - Rhythm Jump Studio Rift
Will You Snail? - Disco of Doom
PVZ2 - Modern Day Mid Wave B
Crypt of the NecroDancer - Deep Sea Bass (Chipzel Remix)
A Hat in Time - Killing Two Birds
Dicey Dungeons Reunion - Swing Me One More Six
PVZ2 - Modern Day Mid First Wave
Luigi's Mansion 3 - 13F Exterior
Persona 4 - Signs Of Love
Crypt of the NecroDancer - Stone Cold (Chipzel Remix)
Super Mario Bros. Wonder - Castle Bowser Theme
Persona 5 - Triumph
Dicey Dungeons Halloween - Cutscene (cheery)
Dicey Dungeons - Beginner's Luck
Agent_Jo - Sea Garden (From "Sea Garden", the game this video is about, silly)
Agent_Jo - Fools Gambit
